description: Perched on the 3rd floor of a boutique building built in 2020, this bright & sunny corner PH home is a treat! Ideal open concept floor plan allows the kitchen/living/dining to flow seamlessly while offering access to a large private deck through glass sliding doors just off the living area. An extension of the living space, the deck is a little city oasis w/distant views of Back Bay & surrounded by greenery for privacy. Crisp, stylish kitchen features stainless steel appliances, custom cabinets & quartz countertops. Large windows throughout & 4 exposures allow natural light to fill the home throughout the day. Primary suite w/exceptional city skyline views features spa-like en-suite bath w/heated floors & step-in shower. Large 2nd bed connects to en-suite Jack & Jill style bath w/step-in shower. Central A/C, hardwood floors, in-unit laundry included. 2 garage parking spots complete this offering on F Street w/close proximity to some of the best restaurants, cafes & bars on Broadway.
